OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,FXavier Ducept, France's junior
OL,8,Fminister for the sea, has criticised
OL,9,Fthe UK for making demands that risk
OL,10,Fthe lives of asylum seekers.
OL,12,FAccording to Le Monde, he told a
OL,13,FFrench parliamentary commission of
OL,14,Finquiry last week: "What we want is
OL,15,Ffor ... the British to contribute to
OL,16,Ffunding interception systems, which
OL,17,Fare very expensive.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
