OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775113301
OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,F"But they must not make this funding
OL,8,Fconditional on a type of efficiency
OL,9,Fthat could be extremely dangerous for
OL,10,Fmigrants, for the (security) services,
OL,11,Fand for France ... rescue comes first.
OL,12,FAnd the law."
