OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,FIn 2025, the UK struck a returns deal
OL,8,Fwith France, whereby migrants ilegally
OL,9,Fentering the UK would be returned to
OL,10,FFrance as a deterrent, whilst those
OL,11,Fwith legitimate links and asylum
OL,12,Fclaims would be exchanged instead.
OL,14,FThis pilot runs until June, when a
OL,15,Fpermanent deal may be agreed.
OL,17,FWhile the number of arrivals has
OL,18,Ffallen so far this year, the number of
OL,19,Fmigrants arriving per boat has climbed
OL,20,Fto a new high, averaging 63 people on
OL,21,Fboard each one over January to March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775113301
OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,FThe average across the whole of last
OL,8,Fyear was 62 migrants per boat, while
OL,9,Fthe figure for January-March 2025 was
OL,10,F56.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, two migrants died
OL,13,Fcrossing the English Channel from
OL,14,FFrance, hours after the deal aimed at
OL,15,Freducing the number of departures, was
OL,16,Fdue to expire.
OL,18,FSix others were rescued, with one of
OL,19,Fthem rushed to hospital for further
OL,20,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775113301
OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,FThe French maritime prefecture said
OL,8,Fthe small boat headed towards the
OL,9,Fbeach at Gravelines, near Calais, at
OL,10,Faround 9.30am on Wednesday, where a
OL,11,Fgroup of about 30 migrants was waiting
OL,12,Ffor it.
OL,14,FResponders pulled eight people onto a
OL,15,Frescue boat when they got into
OL,16,Fdifficulty, and a medical team was
OL,17,Ftaken out to meet them ` but two
OL,18,Fpeople could not be saved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775113301
OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,FMigrants, including children, were
OL,8,Fseen struggling to board the small
OL,9,Fboat, while at least 12 French police
OL,10,Fofficers were present on the beach
OL,11,Farea at the time.
OL,13,FSteve Smith, chief executive of
OL,14,Frefugee charity Care4Calais, said: "It
OL,15,Fis a tragedy that another two lives
OL,16,Fhave been lost to our deadly border.
OL,18,F"That this latest tragedy comes hours
OL,19,Fafter the Home Secretary agreed an
OL,20,Fextension to their brutal border deal
OL,21,Fwith France, is telling.
OL,26,@vD@dOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
