OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775113301
OL,3,CTwo migrants die crossing Channel as
OL,4,Coverall small boat journeys down by a
OL,5,Cthird
OL,7,F"Our border is a silent killer through
OL,8,Fpolitical choice.
OL,10,F"The UK-French agreements on border
OL,11,Fsecurity do not work as a deterrent,
OL,12,Fbut they do kill.
OL,14,F"If the UK government wanted to save
OL,15,Flives, and end Channel crossings, they
OL,16,Fwould immediately introduce safe
OL,17,Froutes for refugees to claim asylum in
OL,18,Fthe UK."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUzD@HO]
